n. Meanwhile, Union Home Minister Amit Shah called Chief Minister A. Revanth Reddy. Mr. Reddy told him about the measures taken to reduce loss of lives. Mr. Shah assured complete cooperation in extending assistance.","Incessant rains in Telangana have claimed at least nine lives, with some victims swept away while crossing streams. Among the deceased were Yakub and Saidabee, while their son Sharif was rescued by a drone-dropped life jacket. Khammam, Mahabubabad, and other areas were severely affected, with road connectivity disrupted. Union Home Minister Amit Shah assured full cooperation in assistance efforts following a discussion with Chief Minister A. Revanth Reddy.",Local News,2024-09-02 00:00:00
