 to Covid-19, the date of audit has been extended to December 31.” The Cabinet also extended the term of the mayor and deputy mayor by three months, stating that it is not possible to hold polls amid the pandemic.","This news falls under the ""Local News"" or ""Regional News"" category, as it pertains to specific events and decisions affecting the districts of Raigad, Ratnagiri, and Sindhudurg in Maharashtra, India. Additionally, it may also be categorized under ""Environment"" due to the impact of Cyclone Nisarga on local agriculture.",Local News,2024-07-24 00:00:00
