 subscriptions from Rs 32 to Rs 40. - Association demands withdrawal of the introduced hikes from this month. - Concerns raised about viability with expenses higher than revenue. - Demand for rationalization of entertainment tax imposed by the state government on cable operators. - Tax is Rs 50 per connection annually, claimed to be the highest in the country compared to Rs 7 in UP and Rs 20 in Delhi.",Local News,2004-01-05 00:00:00
