e Minister Narendra Modi before a grand celebration in Mumbai. Bumrah's homecoming in Ahmedabad was marked by a touching moment captured in a viral video where he embraced his mother amidst a warm reception from neighbors, who showered him with flower petals. Bumrah's stellar performance, including 15 wickets at an average of 8.26, earned him the Player of the Tournament title for his pivotal role in India's triumph.",Sports,2024-07-07 00:00:00
