s after rainstorms, leaving many without electricity, even before the monsoon has fully set in. HBR Layout residents are similarly affected, experiencing frequent and unscheduled power cuts up to ten times a day. The outages are causing significant disruptions for those reliant on electricity for their livelihoods, such as business owners and professionals working from home. Despite these challenges, residents report that Bescom has not been responsive or communicative about the power cuts. The situation is particularly challenging for students like those in Kanaknagar, who are struggling to prepare for exams amidst the frequent power failures.",Weather,2013-03-23 00:00:00
