 heartland, Saskatchewan is fast becoming a favourite destination for travellers from across the world","Schools interested in participating in Canadian education programs can reach out to the Canadian Education Centre (CEC), India, for assistance in nominating eligible students. Saskatchewan, located in Canada's heartland, is gaining popularity as a preferred destination for global travelers.",Education,2008-01-14 00:00:00
