ts on May 18th and 19th from 7 PM onwards on Mazhavil Manorama, Mazhavil Manorama HD and Mazhavil Manorama International. Along with the Prime sponsor Malabar Gold and Diamonds, brands such as Popees Baby Care Products, Fogg (Vini Cosmetics Private Limited), Swayamvara Silks, Pittappillil Agencies and m4marry.com are the other sponsors.","Mazhavil Manorama, a prominent general entertainment channel (GEC) in Kerala, hosted its inaugural ""Mazhavil Entertainment Awards"" to celebrate creative excellence in the entertainment industry. The event featured performances from stars within and outside the Malayalam film industry. Honors included ""All-time Entertainer"" for singer K. J. Yesudas, ""Ultimate Entertainers"" for actor Mohanlal and filmmaker Priyadarshan, and awards for Best Actor (shared by Tovino Thomas and Fahad Fazil), Best Actress (Aishwarya Lakshmi), and Best Director (Prithviraj for ""Lucifer""). Bollywood celebrities, including Bipasha Basu and Sonakshi Sinha, added glamour to the event. The telecast will be in two parts on May 18th and 19th on Mazhavil Manorama.",Entertainment,2019-05-14 00:00:00
