ogressive ideas, which focused on social development, were praised by Minister for Transport Antony Raju and CPI(M) state secretary M. V. Govindan. Finance Minister K. N. Balagopal credited Narayana Guru with preventing communalism in Kerala and stressed the guru's clear vision of the world. However, BJP state president K. Surendran expressed concerns about attempts to manipulate the guru's philosophy. KPCC president K. Sudhakaran acknowledged Narayana Guru's pivotal role in promoting the concept of equality. Film director Shaji N. Karun emphasized the importance of values in ensuring social justice, crediting Narayana Guru for eloquently defining these values.",Human Interest,2023-01-01 00:00:00
