me Minister Benjamin Netanyahu’s office said. The first hostages to be released are women and children.“The government of Israel is committed to bringing all of the hostages home. Tonight, the government approved the outline for the first stage of achieving this goal,” the office said in a statement.","Elon Musk's social media firm, X Corp, has announced that all revenue from advertising and subscriptions related to the ongoing war in Gaza will be donated to hospitals in Israel and the Red Cross/Crescent in the Hamas-controlled region. Musk addressed concerns about funds potentially reaching Hamas by stating that the company would track how the money is spent, going through the Red Cross/Crescent. He also expressed openness to better ideas for helping victims and emphasized the importance of caring for the innocent, irrespective of race, creed, or religion. This announcement preceded Israel's approval of a four-day ceasefire deal with Hamas, involving the release of hostages in the Gaza Strip.",International News,2023-11-22 00:00:00
